In case anyone else happens to be looking for the same thing, here's what I came up with for finding the cargo size of an item within 4_World
``` 
int GetParentCargoCapacity(EntityAI parent)
    {
        CargoBase parentCargo = parent.GetInventory().GetCargo();
        return parentCargo.GetWidth() * parentCargo.GetHeight();
    }
```
